				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">FM and LDON hards<a name="67227"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Oct 17 04 2:09 PM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>I don't have any experience doing LDON hards as a bard, but I do have a lot of experience as an enchanter.  I recall lull being extremely unreliable, and I was wondering how it went pulling as a bard.  How many fades do you have to typically blow through when pulling on a hard?  How much of a mana pool do you need minimum, and how much FT?</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="SmallText"><hr size="1" align="left" width="15%"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1120064" target=_new>Ashtaroth</a>, 63 Bard<br>
