				<td><img src="/skins/default/images/user_IsOffline.gif" alt="Lendias is not online. Last active: 5/19/2005 6:51:03 PM" border="0" />&nbsp;<a class="SmallBoldText" href="/User/UserProfile.aspx?UserName=Lendias">Lendias</a><br></td>
