				<td colspan="2"><span>In roughly 100 hard LDONs, I never did one with an enchanter at all.  Bring two or three, mez all but one, and that works pretty much everywhere.  Lull is not totally useless -- crank up your charisma so you don't automatically agro on a resist, and it will work roughly 1/3 to 1/2 the time.  If you have two mobs in close proximity, mez one and then fade during the pull - that can split very cleanly.  Feed your tank the target you want them on for a rough pull -- say &quot;assist me now&quot; then change targets afterward to get the one you plan to mez.  Communication with your group is key.</span></td>
